Package: arrow.gh.cache
Title: GitHub API Cache for apache/arrow
Version: 0.0.1
Description: Builds a parquet-format cache of issues, pull requests, and
    comments from the apache/arrow repository. Writes are published as
    assets on the cache-latest GitHub Release of this repo.
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    arrow,
    cli,
    dplyr,
    fs,
    gh,
    purrr,
    tibble
